### KYC Verification — KycVerificationAgent
### POST /api/kyc/verify
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Low-risk case: straightforward clean customer → direct APPROVE path
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/kyc/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "CUST-001",
  "fullName": "Anna Müller",
  "dateOfBirth": "1985-03-12",
  "nationality": "German",
  "occupation": "Software Engineer",
  "sourceOfFunds": "Salary"
}

###

### High-risk case: PEP match → enhanced due diligence path
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/kyc/verify
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "CUST-002",
  "fullName": "Viktor Petrov",
